title: Samsonite: We Carry the World – Innovator, Savitha Sridharan (:15)
description: At Samsonite, we don’t just help you carry things. Sure, the ‘things’ in your backpacks, business bags and luggage are often inanimate objects but they are so much more than just things. They’re tools, hopes, dreams, inspirations and ambitions. People use Samsonite to carry their world around with them as they go about conquering it. That’s what we carry. We carry ways for people to get to the places they need to go — in life and their careers. So no, we don’t just carry things. #WeCarryTheWorld
